{"tid":1541230,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【日本平野玲子：會與香港人戰至最後，爭取五大訴求】一定要將自由傳比下一代！","createTime":"2019-09-04T13:59:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T09:11:10.000Z","uid":14328,"like":65,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"6b0653b80d524faca9b10779e3406acf5eb7e9ee","tid":1541230,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:59:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/04/FaUdOC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F04%2FFaUdOC.png&h=90e0f1e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/suzutaro18\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsuzutaro18&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJAQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=ab2474f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/suzutaro18</a><br />\n<br />\n日本人真係高汁民族，一眼就睇穿林鄭把戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家一定要頂撚住！食住個勢！敵退我追！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n９月８日<br />\n美國領事館<br />\n百萬人請求通過＜＜香港人權與民主法案＞＞<br />\n<br />\n中國要接收清政府嘅香港！<br />\n就應該承擔埋清政府留低既一萬億美元債！<br />\n如果唔係既話，將香港交返比英國／美國<br />\n同埋取消一中承認台灣係國家！"},{"pid":"61ca323c722b87b42c16c7118f6c1f593e80b7a8","tid":1541230,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:04:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1885b9602293731ca09df4581d2109fe893f91a7","tid":1541230,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:07:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c572a053f5fdbaf0fcbdf6eeb9890876ea3592","tid":1541230,"uid":277084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:11:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b8526693a973c4378268d93610c1721bfe39bb","tid":1541230,"uid":8647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited